(Commencement) Order 2024.

title: on me by section 1(2) of the Road Traffic Act 2016 (No. 21 of 2016), hereby
heading: 2. The 1st day of October 2024 is appointed as the day on which Part 2 of
text_raw:
2. The 1st day of October 2024 is appointed as the day on which Part 2 of 

the Road Traffic Act 2016 (No. 21 of 2016) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

14 June, 2024. 

EAMON RYAN, 

Minister of Transport. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 18th June, 2024.
